Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:46.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}仿佛一望无际
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.33,0:22:53.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}悲伤已烟消云散
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.38,0:23:00.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}为了不让这份笑容黯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:08.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}我会一直在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.06,0:23:12.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}没有泪水的明天过后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.69,0:23:16.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}会有温柔的未来等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.36,0:23:23.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}即便是微弱的希望 也相信着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.45,0:23:27.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Reason of life一定能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.04,0:23:30.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Feel you heart 只属于自己的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:35.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}迷茫的时候携手前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:37.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}在现实(现在)中Survive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:41.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Reason of life会和你一同发现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.47,0:23:50.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}生而为人的证明 与促成邂逅的点滴
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.36,0:22:36.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}(Stay with you forever…)
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.08,0:22:46.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}どこまでも続くような
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.33,0:22:53.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}悲しみはどこにもない
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.38,0:23:00.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}その笑顔 曇らないように
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.22,0:23:08.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}いつでもそばにいるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.06,0:23:12.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}涙のない明日の先に
